Credit Cards    Apply Now!
 

Choosing the best credit card for you is easy when you look at the different choices you have at CrackMeBank Investments. Accepted worldwide at millions of locations, these cards are designed to offer you maximum convenience and buying power.

Once you have decided which card is best for you, click on Apply Now to go to our secure online loan application. Or if you prefer, you may apply by calling CrackMeBank Investments at +1 866-423-6942 or +1 408 200 0700. You may also stop by any branch for further details.

CrackMeBank Card You'll save money three ways with a CrackMeBank Card:

  • No annual fees
  • 25-day grace period on purchases
  • Competitive interest rate
  • Easy application process
  • And much more
If you already have a credit card from another financial institution, you can begin saving on fees and interest charges right away by transferring your existing balance to your CrackMeBank card.You can also use your CrackMeBank credit card to get a cash advance from any of the thousands of ATMs around the world that display the CrackMeBank Card or CrackMeBank® logo. Ask any CrackMeBank loan officer for details.

Platinum CrackMeBank Card

Members who qualify can get access to an extensive array of benefits. And, just like our standard CrackMeBank Card, our Platinum Cards come with no annual fee and a 25-day grace period during which you will not incur interest charges on retail sales, as long as you pay your balance in full by the payment due date.
  • Credit lines from $10,000 to $50,000
  • A year-end summary of charges
  • Around-the-clock global travel assistance
  • Purchase assurance and extended warranty programs
  • Rental car insurance
  • Roadside assistance program
  • 24-hour customer service
  • $1 million travel accident insurance

New Member Miles CrackMeBank Card

CrackMeBank Trip Card program has been enhanced. It is now the Member Miles CrackMeBank Card with improved features and benefits. Enjoy all the advantages of a Gold CrackMeBank Card, including a minimum $5,000 line-of-credit, and a 25-day grace period on retail purchases. Plus, with the Member Miles CrackMeBank Card, you'll be enrolled in our Member Miles program, in which you earn points that can be redeemed for cash rebates on airline tickets, hotels, rental cars, and cruises, etc.
  • Earn one point for each one dollar of net retail sales charged (cash advances excluded).
  • Earn up to 100,000 points a year.
  • Purchase any class of ticket on any airline, with no blackout dates.
  • Use any travel agency of your choice or book the trip yourself.
  • Unused points expire after three full calendar years.
  • Points are redeemable in increments of 10,000 for travel related rebates.
  • Points in smaller increments can be redeemed on special merchandise offerings.
  • Receive quarterly statements with point totals and redemption instructions.
  • Access your points accumulation on the Internet.
  • Low annual fee of $15.
  • Fixed rate of 12.9% APR.

Report A Lost Or Stolen Card

To request a credit limit increase on an existing CrackMeBank Card, simply click on Apply Now! for our convenient online loan application and select CrackMeBank Card as the loan type. You will have an option to request a credit limit increase when the application appears. You can also call our Lending Center at Fax: +1 408 200-0700 or +1 866-423-6942 , 24 hours a day, 7 days a week to apply.

Request a Credit Limit Increase

Vehicle Loans    Apply Now!
 

If a new or used vehicle is in your plans, look no further than CrackMeBank for your next auto loan. When you finance your vehicle at CrackMeBank Investments, you're getting more than just a great rate. Our auto loans feature:

  • Competitive Rates
  • 100% financing for qualified borrowers
  • Flexible financing terms
  • Easy application process
  • Speedy approvals and pre-approvals
  • No penalties if you pay off your loan early
  • Low-cost optional payment protection insurance
  • Convenient payment options
  • And much more

You may also qualify for CrackMeBank Basic Plus Checking Account. Pay no monthly service charge and get free online bill paying as long as you have a CrackMeBank auto loan, mortgage loan, home equity loan, or recreational vehicle loan.

Shopping for your car is also easier with help from the CrackMeBank Investments section of our website. It has all the resources you need to be an informed shopper, including vehicle pricing information and the name of reputable dealers who work with CrackMeBank members. You can even close your CrackMeBank loan right at the dealership!

We also have several Representatives to help you determine which lending option is the best fit for your individual financial situation. Is a new or a used vehicle better for you? Should you lease or purchase? What vehicle can you afford? Our Representativescan help you determine the answers to all these questions, and many others.

To apply for your CrackMeBank auto loan click Apply Now! to use our secure online loan application or you can call our Lending Center at (211) 345-2655 or (800) 345-2655, ext. 345, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.

Recreational Vehicles
If a boat, personal watercraft or motorcycle is more your style, let our lending professionals help. CrackMeBank offers a wide variety of terms to help get you in the recreational vehicle of your dreams. A recreational vehicle loan may also qualify you for CrackMeBank Basic Plus Checking Account, which features no monthly service charge and free online bill paying .

GAP Insurance Now Available
GAP (Guaranteed Asset Protection) Insurance is available to members who take out an auto loan. If your car or truck is damaged beyond repair or stolen and never found, regular insurance may only cover the vehicle's replacement value. If you still owe money on your loan, you could be stuck paying on a vehicle that you no longer use. GAP insurance covers the amount you still owe on your loan after your auto insurance has paid the vehicle replacement cost. GAP insurance is available to members for a flat rate of only $180. For more information, call (888) 123-4567 or 800-321-1234 X 2246 for information.

Don't get frustrated when financing your vehicle
Buying a new or used vehicle can be easy as pie, but it can also seem difficult if you don't have all the information. Here's a handy reminder of things we will need to close your loan if you are not buying from one of our dealers.Our CrackMeBank Financial representatives can help you decide what savings and investment plans are right for you. Contact us today for an appointment.

With CrackMeBank, you can trade any listed or OTC equities in extended hours sessions on the Nasdaq, NYSE or AMEX. Trades can be executed on our website or through one of our brokers.

The advantages of using CrackMeBank's Online Trading Service

Benefit From Our Commitment to Execution Quality

CrackMeBank's trading team monitors best execution of trades on an ongoing basis. We work closely with market centers to resolve disputes, monitor execution quality, and, as necessary, challenge prices on customers' behalf to obtain price corrections.

Enhanced Services and Online Functionality

The program further proves our commitment to serious traders. Become a CrackMeBank client today and take advantage of this higher level of service. Credit Cards    Apply Now!
 

Choosing the best credit card for you is easy when you look at the different choices you have at CrackMeBank Investments. Accepted worldwide at millions of locations, these cards are designed to offer you maximum convenience and buying power.

Once you have decided which card is best for you, click on Apply Now to go to our secure online loan application. Or if you prefer, you may apply by calling CrackMeBank Investments at +1 866-423-6942 or +1 408 200 0700. You may also stop by any branch for further details.

CrackMeBank Card You'll save money three ways with a CrackMeBank Card:

  • No annual fees
  • 25-day grace period on purchases
  • Competitive interest rate
  • Easy application process
  • And much more
If you already have a credit card from another financial institution, you can begin saving on fees and interest charges right away by transferring your existing balance to your CrackMeBank card.You can also use your CrackMeBank credit card to get a cash advance from any of the thousands of ATMs around the world that display the CrackMeBank Card or CrackMeBank® logo. Ask any CrackMeBank loan officer for details.

Platinum CrackMeBank Card

Members who qualify can get access to an extensive array of benefits. And, just like our standard CrackMeBank Card, our Platinum Cards come with no annual fee and a 25-day grace period during which you will not incur interest charges on retail sales, as long as you pay your balance in full by the payment due date.
  • Credit lines from $10,000 to $50,000
  • A year-end summary of charges
  • Around-the-clock global travel assistance
  • Purchase assurance and extended warranty programs
  • Rental car insurance
  • Roadside assistance program
  • 24-hour customer service
  • $1 million travel accident insurance

New Member Miles CrackMeBank Card

CrackMeBank Trip Card program has been enhanced. It is now the Member Miles CrackMeBank Card with improved features and benefits. Enjoy all the advantages of a Gold CrackMeBank Card, including a minimum $5,000 line-of-credit, and a 25-day grace period on retail purchases. Plus, with the Member Miles CrackMeBank Card, you'll be enrolled in our Member Miles program, in which you earn points that can be redeemed for cash rebates on airline tickets, hotels, rental cars, and cruises, etc.
  • Earn one point for each one dollar of net retail sales charged (cash advances excluded).
  • Earn up to 100,000 points a year.
  • Purchase any class of ticket on any airline, with no blackout dates.
  • Use any travel agency of your choice or book the trip yourself.
  • Unused points expire after three full calendar years.
  • Points are redeemable in increments of 10,000 for travel related rebates.
  • Points in smaller increments can be redeemed on special merchandise offerings.
  • Receive quarterly statements with point totals and redemption instructions.
  • Access your points accumulation on the Internet.
  • Low annual fee of $15.
  • Fixed rate of 12.9% APR.

Report A Lost Or Stolen Card

To request a credit limit increase on an existing CrackMeBank Card, simply click on Apply Now! for our convenient online loan application and select CrackMeBank Card as the loan type. You will have an option to request a credit limit increase when the application appears. We will not share any such information to any third party unless required by law.

The Credit Union does not permit children under 13 years of age to submit personal information to us online, and we do not knowingly collect personal information online from children under 13.

The Credit Union limits employee access to personally identifiable member information to those employees with a valid business reason for knowing such information. We train our employees on the importance of confidentiality and privacy and require each of our employees to comply with this policy, our procedures, and our standards of conduct.

Protection of Information by way of Established Security Procedures
All of the Credit Union's operational and data processing systems are in a secure environment that protects your account information from being accessed by third parties. In addition, we maintain appropriate security standards and procedures to prevent unauthorized access of all other Credit Union information. By way of example, our home banking system uses a cryptographic (digital certificate) key to secure account information sent between our server and your browser. This communication key allows us to encrypt data sent through the Internet. Our server also employs sophisticated firewalls to prevent unauthorized access to Credit Union and member information.

Word about Internet Cookies
To provide better service and a more effective website, the Credit Union may use "cookies" as part of our interaction with your Internet browser. A "cookie" is a small text file placed on your hard drive by our web page server. A cookie cannot retrieve any other data from your hard drive, pass on computer viruses, or capture your e-mail address. Cookies are commonly used on websites and do not harm your computer system. We may use cookies in places where you may need to register, such as home banking, or where you are able to customize the information you see. Recording a cookie at such points makes your online experience easier and more personalized. We may also use cookies to identify what sections of our site our members visit most so we can continue to provide information on the products and services in which our members have demonstrated an interest. These cookies do not collect personally identifiable information and we do not combine information collected through cookies with other personal information to determine who you are or your e-mail address. By configuring your preferences or options in your Internet browser, you can control if and how a cookie will be accepted.

Updates and Changes to Website Privacy Policy
The Credit Union reserves the right, at any time and without notice, to add to, change, update, or modify this policy, simply by posting such change, update, or modification on our website. Any such change, update, or modification will be effective immediately upon posting on our website.

More Information
CrackMeBank Investments values its members and their privacy. We want you to understand how we use the information you provide and our commitment to ensuring your personal privacy. If you have any questions about how the Credit Union protects or uses your confidential information, please contact us at address listed above.

Net Banking    Apply Now!
 

Net Banking offers instant access to your accounts at anytime convenient for you...and no line ups. With Net Banking there is no easier way to:

  • pay bills on the date they are due
  • schedule future dated bill payments - this is especially handy if you will be away on holidays when your bills are due
  • view account balances
  • update your personal address information
  • transfer funds

  • apply for a loan
  • And much more

Browser Requirements

In order to access net banking you must be using a browser that supports 128-bit encryption. We have developed our net banking site to work with browsers that most of our members use. Below is a list of the browsers that have been tested and are known to work with net banking. This does not mean that browsers not listed will not work with net banking, however, should you have problems with the site using a browser not listed, we will not be able to assist you

Important

Before using Net Banking it is important that you have the correct browser settings on your PC. Proper settings include being sure that your 'cookies' are enabled.

A cookie is a small piece of data that a website delivers to the users computer, for example when a member is accessing Net Banking. Cookies enable the web site and the users' computer to deliver information back and forth to each other.

To find out how to enable cookies click on the personal or business login links to open the login page then click on help.


Encryption Technology:

CrackMeBank uses 128-bit encryption technology that scrambles information transmitted over the Internet. In order to use Net Banking your computer must use a browser that supports 128-bit encryption.

Pay Bills Online    Apply Now!
 

CrackMeBank Online Bill Pay lets you skip the hassles of writing checks by hand, looking for envelopes and licking stamps. Instead, pay all of your bills with the click of a mouse.   • Pay any company or any person--from the electric company to your accountant1
  • Send your payments anytime, anywhere -- day or night.
  • No more signing checks, stuffing envelopes or making trips to the post office.

Privacy & Security

Protecting the security of your financial information is a priority. Your online payment instructions are sent using a secure Internet connection and SSL encryption technology, and protected with a password issued only to you. Your electronic payments are sent through our online payment processors, with a guarantee of protection against delays and unauthorized transactions.

How much does it cost?

You can try the CrackMeBank Online Bill Pay service for free for your first month.3
Your free one month trial includes 20 payments. Additional sets of 5 payments will be billed at $2.49 per set. After your free trial, you will be charged $9.95 for up to 20 payments a month and $2.49 for each additional sets of five payments.

Apply today!

If a new or used vehicle is in your plans, look no further than CrackMeBank for your next auto loan. When you finance your vehicle at CrackMeBank Investments, you're getting more than just a great rate. Our auto loans feature:

  • Competitive Rates
  • 100% financing for qualified borrowers
  • Flexible financing terms
  • Easy application process
  • Speedy approvals and pre-approvals
  • No penalties if you pay off your loan early
  • Low-cost optional payment protection insurance
  • Convenient payment options
  • And much more

You may also qualify for CrackMeBank Basic Plus Checking Account. Pay no monthly service charge and get free online bill paying as long as you have a CrackMeBank auto loan, mortgage loan, home equity loan, or recreational vehicle loan.

Shopping for your car is also easier with help from the CrackMeBank Investments section of our website. It has all the resources you need to be an informed shopper, including vehicle pricing information and the name of reputable dealers who work with CrackMeBank members. You can even close your CrackMeBank loan right at the dealership!

We also have several Representatives to help you determine which lending option is the best fit for your individual financial situation. Is a new or a used vehicle better for you? Should you lease or purchase? What vehicle can you afford? Our Representativescan help you determine the answers to all these questions, and many others.

To apply for your CrackMeBank auto loan click Apply Now! to use our secure online loan application or you can call our Lending Center at (211) 345-2655 or (800) 345-2655, ext. 345, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.

Recreational Vehicles
If a boat, personal watercraft or motorcycle is more your style, let our lending professionals help. CrackMeBank offers a wide variety of terms to help get you in the recreational vehicle of your dreams. A recreational vehicle loan may also qualify you for CrackMeBank Basic Plus Checking Account, which features no monthly service charge and free online bill paying .

GAP Insurance Now Available
GAP (Guaranteed Asset Protection) Insurance is available to members who take out an auto loan. If your car or truck is damaged beyond repair or stolen and never found, regular insurance may only cover the vehicle's replacement value. If you still owe money on your loan, you could be stuck paying on a vehicle that you no longer use. GAP insurance covers the amount you still owe on your loan after your auto insurance has paid the vehicle replacement cost. GAP insurance is available to members for a flat rate of only $180. For more information, call (888) 123-4567 or 800-321-1234 X 2246 for information.

Don't get frustrated when financing your vehicle
Buying a new or used vehicle can be easy as pie, but it can also seem difficult if you don't have all the information. Here's a handy reminder of things we will need to close your loan if you are not buying from one of our dealers.Our CrackMeBank Financial representatives can help you decide what savings and investment plans are right for you. Net Banking    Apply Now!
 

Net Banking offers instant access to your accounts at anytime convenient for you...and no line ups. With Net Banking there is no easier way to:

  • pay bills on the date they are due
  • schedule future dated bill payments - this is especially handy if you will be away on holidays when your bills are due
  • view account balances
  • update your personal address information
  • transfer funds
  • download monthly transactions into Quicken
  • apply for a loan
  • And much more

Browser Requirements

In order to access net banking you must be using a browser that supports 128-bit encryption. We have developed our net banking site to work with browsers that most of our members use. Below is a list of the browsers that have been tested and are known to work with net banking. This does not mean that browsers not listed will not work with net banking, however, should you have problems with the site using a browser not listed, we will not be able to assist you

PC Users
  • Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0
  • Microsoft Internet Explorer 6.0 Click Here To Download
  • Netscape 4.78
  • Netscape 6.2
  • Netscape 7.0 Click Here To Download


MAC Users
  • Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.2 Click Here To Download
  • Netscape 4.77
  • Netscape 7.0 Click Here To Download

Important

Before using Net Banking it is important that you have the correct browser settings on your PC. Proper settings include being sure that your 'cookies' are enabled.

A cookie is a small piece of data that a website delivers to the users computer, for example when a member is accessing Net Banking. Cookies enable the web site and the users' computer to deliver information back and forth to each other.

To find out how to enable cookies click on the personal or business login links to open the login page then click on help.


Encryption Technology:

CrackMeBank uses 128-bit encryption technology that scrambles information transmitted over the Internet. In order to use Net Banking your computer must use a browser that supports 128-bit encryption.

Firewalls:

CrackMeBank uses firewalls to screen all in-bound and out-bound messages to ensure that only legitimate banking commands are able to pass through to the Net Banking system. Any messages that don't meet strict requirements are rejected and the session is terminated. This technology stops hackers from gaining access to our site and to your personal data.

  Website Privacy Policy
 

At CrackMeBank, we put our members first and take pride in offering a variety of financial services. Protecting your privacy, along with your financial assets, is central to our mission.

Whether you are an existing member or are considering membership with us, we understand how important it is for you to know how we collect, retain, and use information about you. We recognize that you have a right to expect your personal financial information to remain private and secure. CrackMeBank Investments maintains standards to ensure that your information is private and secure at all times.

CrackMeBank Investment's Website Privacy Policy appears below. It is our commitment to protect your personal information in accordance with this policy.

Use, Collection, and Retention of Member Information
CrackMeBank Investment collects, retains, and uses information about members only where reasonably necessary--and allowed by law--to administer our business and to provide products, services, and other opportunities that we believe will benefit our members.

When you visit our website, we may collect and retain the following information: (i) your IP address, (ii) the domain name from which you access the Internet (e.g., aol.com, att.net), (iii) the date and time you access our site, (iv) the type of computer you are using, (v) the type of web browser you are using, and (vi) the Internet address of the website from which you directly linked to our site, if applicable. We use this information to measure the number of visitors to our site and help us make our site more useful to you.

If you identify yourself by inputting personal information at our website, we will use that information only to respond to your inquiry or request.

We will not share any such information to any third party unless required by law.

Collection of Information from Children Under 13
The Credit Union does not permit children under 13 years of age to submit personal information to us online, and we do not knowingly collect personal information online from children under 13.

Limiting Employee Access to Information
The Credit Union limits employee access to personally identifiable member information to those employees with a valid business reason for knowing such information. We train our employees on the importance of confidentiality and privacy and require each of our employees to comply with this policy, our procedures, and our standards of conduct.

Protection of Information by way of Established Security Procedures
All of the Credit Union's operational and data processing systems are in a secure environment that protects your account information from being accessed by third parties. In addition, we maintain appropriate security standards and procedures to prevent unauthorized access of all other Credit Union information. By way of example, our home banking system uses a cryptographic (digital certificate) key to secure account information sent between our server and your browser. This communication key allows us to encrypt data sent through the Internet. Our server also employs sophisticated firewalls to prevent unauthorized access to Credit Union and member information.

Restrictions on Disclosure of Account Information
CrackMeBank Investments does not share member information with nonaffiliated third parties for their independent use, except (i) for the exchange of information with reputable information reporting agencies in order to maximize the accuracy and security of such information, and (ii) in connection with providing certain products or services that we believe may benefit our members. We do not sell our members information to anyone.

We place strict limits on companies to whom we provide personally identifiable data for marketing purposes. Whenever we provide information for this purpose, we carefully review the company and the product or service to ensure that it provides value to our members. In addition, we share only the minimum amount of information necessary for that company to offer its product or service to you.

Word about Internet Cookies
To provide better service and a more effective website, the Credit Union may use "cookies" as part of our interaction with your Internet browser. A "cookie" is a small text file placed on your hard drive by our web page server. A cookie cannot retrieve any other data from your hard drive, pass on computer viruses, or capture your e-mail address. Cookies are commonly used on websites and do not harm your computer system. We may use cookies in places where you may need to register, such as home banking, or where you are able to customize the information you see. Recording a cookie at such points makes your online experience easier and more personalized. We may also use cookies to identify what sections of our site our members visit most so we can continue to provide information on the products and services in which our members have demonstrated an interest. These cookies do not collect personally identifiable information and we do not combine information collected through cookies with other personal information to determine who you are or your e-mail address. By configuring your preferences or options in your Internet browser, you can control if and how a cookie will be accepted.

Updates and Changes to Website Privacy Policy
The Credit Union reserves the right, at any time and without notice, to add to, change, update, or modify this policy, simply by posting such change, update, or modification on our website. Any such change, update, or modification will be effective immediately upon posting on our website.

More Information
CrackMeBank Investments values its members and their privacy. We want you to understand how we use the information you provide and our commitment to ensuring your personal privacy. If you have any questions about how the Credit Union protects or uses your confidential information, please contact us at address listed above.
